{
  "stem": "22883.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he even volunteered to-- to go with us together to Vienna because he had still, in Vienna, a lot of friends.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, this way we boarded the-- I don't remember, the next day or after two days, we went by train to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was working before with a group of people-- men from Czechoslovakia and from Poland in a-- in the newspaper, a Vienna newspaper.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were quartering in a-- taken by the government, the German government, a-- a restaurant.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The owner of the restaurant was [SIGHS] in Army, and the whole restaurant was used as the dormitory for those workers of the newspaper.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Because of-- of quite a lot of those workers were from Czechoslovakia, and from Vienna to Czechoslovakia is very close, so every weekend, they were going to-- to Bratislava [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to see their families.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, in this dormitory there were empty beds.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in this way, this-- this guy, this Polish man, he-- he-- he knew everybody there, and he had the access.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think he had the key, even.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, we-- the-- for-- through this weekend, we slept in this dormitory.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after-- after-- after the weekend, we had to find out some place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we got a-- a room in a hotel in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And interesting that because, well, we were always afraid that the-- maybe the police or something was looking for-- asking for our documents and so on.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So anyway, this hotel gave us the room without any problems, but of course, they-- they could not be responsible for our safety.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So anyway, one night, we were waked up of terrible noise.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I thought, and Liliana thought-- thought too that somebody's banging the doors.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
